      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SANDRA KEEPING (7) goes very well this trip starting five times for two wins and two minors. Scored by 3.5 lengths last time (30.71) in a Grade 5 over 525m at Taree Super Track. Makes strong appeal on best. BLAZING PRINCE (2) was below best at his last start when 8th at Dubbo following a second place finish (30.59) at Taree Super Track two back. Likely to play a prominent role. ZIPPING LARGO (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing seventh (30.61) in a Grade 5 at this track. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. FASCINATE JOSIE (3) is another with top-three prospects.",
